Printed at the Central Bank Printing Press, No. 58, Sri Jayewardenepura Mawatha, Rajagiriya and Published by the Central Bank of Sri Lanka, Janadhipathi Mawatha, Colombo 1.
HER EXCELLENCY THE PRESIDENT AND MINISTER OF FINANCE, PLANNING, ETHNIC AFFAIRS AND NATIONAL INTEGRATION, MINISTRY OF FINANCE, PLANNING, ETHNIC AFFAIRS AND NATIONAL INTEGRATION, COLOMBO.

In accordance with the provisions of Section 35(1) of the Monetary Law Act, (Chapter 422), I submit herewith the Forty Fifth Annual Report of the Monetary Board of the Central Bank of Sri Lanka covering the Bank's operations during the year 1994.
Central Bank of Sri Lanka, Colombo.
A.S. JAYAWARDENA Secretary to the Ministry of Finance, Planning, Ethnic Affairs and National Integration
